<exploration xml:id="warm-observa-ladosDesconocidos" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Observa y pregúntate: Lados desconocidos</title>

<statement>
  <p>¿Qué observas? ¿Qué te preguntas?</p>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-148649">
          <shortdescription>Polígono verde en L con medidas en centímetros.</shortdescription>
        </image>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students may notice:</p>
<ul>
      <li>We can break this figure into two rectangles.</li>
      <li>Some of the side lengths are missing.</li>
      <li>Some of the side lengths are given in centimeters.</li>
    </ul>
<p>Students may wonder:</p>
<ul>
      <li>Can we still find the area of this figure?</li>
      <li>Is there a way to find the missing side lengths?</li>
      <li>Is there only one possible number for the missing side lengths?</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


